  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9 \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb\u0db8\u0d9f \u0db1\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Wilgamu Kidney Hospital stops midway",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Wakagadu patients in that area are in dire straits because the construction of the building started at Wilgamuwa Hospital in Matale for blood transfusions for kidney patients has been stopped midway.",
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena had built a new building at Hettipola, Wilgamuwa Hospital and created the necessary environment for conducting clinics for kidney patients.",
        "According to the requests of the people of Wilgamuwa area, under the former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa's program, 90 million rupees was allocated from the Presidential Secretariat to provide a building and sub-equipment necessary for blood transfusions.",
        "According to that, although the construction work of lakhs of medical equipment as well as the building has started, all of it has stopped in the middle because the contractor companies have stopped the construction and left at once.",
        "Since many years the people of this area are suffering seriously from undiagnosed kidney disease, the people of Wilgamuwa, Hadungamuwa Hettipola, Maraka, etc said that every house in that area has one or two kidney patients.",
        "The kidney patients said that they had to travel to hospitals in Mahiyangana, Kandy, Polonnaruwa and Dambulla which are more than a hundred kilometers away from Wilgamuwa area for blood transfusions.",
        "A hospital spokesperson stated that the Wilgamuwa Hospital ambulance will be used to transport patients who have difficulty in walking."
      ],
